----------------------------
--Snake Game README---------
----------------------------


Snake Game requires Node.js and express


To install Node.js please visit:
  - https://nodejs.org/en/


To install express & path using npm:
  - Navigate to the root directory that contains package.json and index.js (ie: */Snake)
  - Run the following command:
	npm install express --save


To run Snake Game using Node.js:
  - Navigate to the root directory that contains package.json and index.js (ie: */Snake)
  - Run the following command:
	node index.js
  - Open a web browser and navigate to: http://localhost:3000

